{"tid":2495856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓花旗銀行「退出」計劃還沒定　工會已揚言要大罷工","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:45:29.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"189164d8ae0ab2c24b18f240f313c067118f6c8d","tid":2495856,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"《韓國時報》（The Korea Times）報導，花旗已決定退出涵蓋貸款、儲蓄、信用卡等業務的南韓消費金融市場，但花旗當地子公司Citibank Korea的具體「退場」策略仍未確定。Citibank Korea將於4月27日召開董事會討論相關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n然而在開始討論退出策略及業務整頓細節前，Citibank Korea已面臨來自勞方的強烈反彈。1位工會幹部說：「如果Citibank Korea要賣掉或退出這裡的零售銀行業務，將會造成大量失業。為了員工就業保障並保護客戶，我們將反對這樣的舉動。」<br />\n<br />\n據工會方面表示，Citibank Korea在2012年開始整頓消金事業。2011年時Citibank Korea在南韓尚有221處營業辦公室，但截至目前已關閉超過80%，僅剩39處辦公室仍保持營運。<br />\n<br />\n花旗集團的決定，反映了南韓市場的營收衰減。2020年Citibank Korea純益較上年同期銳減32.8%至1878億韓元，其中零售銀行部門純益大減超過50%至148億韓元，與2018年相比更暴減達80%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210419/KUZPPJUYNFCEDKQPCGTHTLLGRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210419%2FKUZPPJUYNFCEDKQPCGTHTLLGRE%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx9C8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=66b7540b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210419%2FKUZPPJUYNFCEDKQPCGTHTLLGRE%2F&h=3cbf7c48\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210419/KUZPPJUYNFCEDKQPCGTHTLLGRE/</a>"},{"pid":"cec85605be8e97b6e373352be601ca5ac07e916b","tid":2495856,"uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"美國佬又搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7611b7d3c4f1dba3b15a3b2a9f998e833562f8","tid":2495856,"uid":130695,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"人地都走，你罷工係罷畀鬼睇 <img src=\